","8. Standard CANopen","9. Návrh bezdrátové sítě standardu ZigBee","10. Simulace datových přenosů v prostředí Matlab - Simulink","11. Distribuovaný komunikační systém vozu Škoda FABIA","12. Deterministické přenosy dat v síti IEEE 802.3","13. Propustnost komunikačních kanálů při vysoké úrovni rušení","14. Vyhodnocení testů, odevzdání sem. prací, zápočet"]},"tutorialsContentsEn":{"line":["1. Introduction, overview or requirements","2. Modem data communication (leased line, PSTN)","3. Power Line Communication","4. Radiomodem networks","5. EIA-232 and EIA-485 interfaces","6. Optical fiber data transmission","7. Basics of distributed systems - Field-Point","8. CANopen standard","9. Design of wireless sensor network (ZigBee) layout","10. Simulation of data communication in Matlab - Simulink","11. Distributed in-vehicle communication in Škoda FABIA","12. Deterministic communication in IEEE 802.3 networks","13. Communication channel throughput upon a high level of electromagnetic disturbance","14. Tests and laboratory reports evaluation, assessment"]}},"editors":{"person":{"@uri":"https://kosapi.feld.cvut.cz/api/2/people/jnovak","@id":"30979000","email":"jnovak@fel.cvut.cz","firstName":"Jiří","login":"jnovak","surname":"Novák","teacher":{"@uri":"https://kosapi.feld.cvut.cz/api/2/people/jnovak/teacher/","@id":"30979000"},"titlePost":"Ph.D.","titlePre":"Doc.Ing."}},"examiners":{"person":[{"@uri":"https://kosapi.feld.cvut.cz/api/2/people/jnovak","@id":"30979000","email":"jnovak@fel.cvut.cz","firstName":"Jiří","login":"jnovak","surname":"Novák","teacher":{"@uri":"https://kosapi.feld.cvut.cz/api/2/people/jnovak/teacher/","@id":"30979000"},"titlePost":"Ph.D.","titlePre":"Doc.Ing."},{"@uri":"https://kosapi.feld.cvut.cz/api/2/people/holubjan","@id":"33570000","email":"holubjan@fel.cvut.cz","firstName":"Jan","login":"holubjan","surname":"Holub","teacher":{"@uri":"https://kosapi.feld.cvut.cz/api/2/people/holubjan/teacher/","@id":"33570000"},"titlePost":"Ph.D.","titlePre":"Doc.Ing."}